    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Techniques and process of covering the surface of pottery, ceramics, or a similar material with a vitreous substance, which is fixed by fusion, usually by heat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
